text: Kim Bong-jo (born 29 May 1942) is a South Korean wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman featherweight at the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1942 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of South Korea Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
